@rithviknishad I would like to work on this
The validation error was occurring because the default values for discounts and taxes were being shown visually but not properly initialized in the form state, resulting in a null value being passed where a string was expected. Updating the form logic to ensure that these fields are initialized correctly as strings resolves the issue

